description:
I like to make art that portrays potential visuals from experiences with psychedelics, I myself have had many experiences so I wanted to bring the beautiful colors to life for others to see.
Now this isn't what everyone experiences on their "trips" but I know when I would close my eyes I would get a rush/burst of colors! It was very intense and would make my heart start beating really fast, but once you just let go and let it swallow you it's unlike anything else! 
Some of, if not all of them, are completely life-changing experiences that I suggest everyone try if they are able to!
*WOW*
